This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for obtaining job description snippets, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The use of neural networks for classification makes cs.LG (Learning) a possible category as well. Additionally, the paper involves computer vision techniques for processing resumes, which makes cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) another possible category. Finally, the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) makes cs.DL (Machine Learning) a possible category as well.
